            <title>[CASSANDRA-15371] Incorrect messaging service version breaks in-JVM upgrade tests on trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15371</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The in-JVM upgrade tests on trunk currently fail because the messaging&lt;br/&gt;
 version for internode messaging is selected as&#160;&lt;tt&gt;MessagingService.current_version&lt;/tt&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
 a regression from the implementation in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15078&quot; title=&quot;Support cross version messaging in in-jvm upgrade dtests&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-15078&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-15078&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
